    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi dear,</p>

<p>I try to set specific dates in a Zend_Date object but I got another date :</p>

<p>Code :</p>

<p>$dayDate = Zend_Date::now();
$dayDate-&gt;setYear(2008);
$dayDate-&gt;setMonth(12);
$dayDate-&gt;setDay(29);
echo $dayDate-&gt;toString('dd/MM/YYYY');</p>

<p>This give me : 29/12/2009 and not 29/12/2009</p>

<p>The problem appears with some date (ex: 31/12/2007, ...)</p>

<p>Thanks for your feedback</p>

<p>--Edit on 2008-08-18
The problem seems to come from toString() function. toArray() function returns right values;</p>

